  • Constructor Details

    • MonthlyParameter

      public MonthlyParameter(String meterName, String[] st) throws Exception
      Load the per meter per month parameters from the appropriate line in the input file. Fragile. Parameters must be in the correct order.
      Parameters:
      meterName - name of the meter that this line pertains to
      st - Array containing month, loss Ratio, Demand Capacity Usage and Demand Critical Peak Usage IN THAT ORDER
      Throws:
      Exception - If any of the required parameters are missing
